rows.label: tev045101_SEL3021
rows.name: Ask Enneana about recent developments.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev045101_MSG0001
rows.name: Cavern Clan likes Ganglion battle suits.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev045101_MSG0002
rows.name:
But Tree Clan are true Prone. We wear clothes made
from skin and bones of beasts.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev045101_MSG0003
rows.name:
Mira has many beasts like simius and terebras.
They yield many such materials.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev045101_MSG0004
rows.name:
I should use these materials.
I would make Prone clothes unique to Mira.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev045101_MSG0009
rows.name: Do Earth aliens love?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev045101_MSG0010
rows.name:
There is male who has stolen my heart.
His very presence warms me.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev045101_MSG0011
rows.name:
While we were in Ganglion captivity,
he alone was source of kindness.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev045101_MSG0012
rows.name: How do I tell him this?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev045101_MSG0013
rows.name:
Should I give him gift from heart?
Will he then see love I hold for him?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev045101_MSG0018
rows.name:
I went to your Armory Alley.
Saw many fascinating Earth clothing styles.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev045101_MSG0019
rows.name: But garment you call "swimsuit" caught my eye![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev045101_MSG0020
rows.name:
It makes wearer beautiful AND is waterproof.
You could look good in rainstorm![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev045101_MSG0021
rows.name: Inventor of "swimsuit" should get many honors![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev045101_MSG0022
rows.name: If only Prone I love could see me in "swimsuit"...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev045101_MSG0027
rows.name:
Prone has no better armor or weapon than own
hardened flesh.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev045101_MSG0028
rows.name: We have no custom of crafting like other aliens.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev045101_MSG0029
rows.name:
You make fine clothes. So do Ma-non.
I am shamed I cannot do same.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev045101_MSG0030
rows.name:
But I do clean and wash better than most Prone!
Maybe I will help in this way.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev045101_MSG1001
rows.name:
Is it true Earth alien females wear special garments for
weddings?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev045101_MSG1002
rows.name:
I watched moving picture of "wedding dress."
I wanted to learn about making Earth-alien clothes.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev045101_MSG1003
rows.name:
White dress is so different from Prone horn-ring of
betrothal and bone crowns![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev045101_MSG1004
rows.name:
Wife of Nemard looked beautiful in white dress.
It made me cry.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev045101_MSG1005
rows.name:
I hope to wear such dress someday.
And to be married to one I love...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev045101_MSG1010
rows.name: Heptana and Nemard make perfect couple.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev045101_MSG1011
rows.name: Gentle Prone like me never had chance with him...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev045101_MSG1012
rows.name: *siiiiiigh*[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev045101_MSG1013
rows.name:
But Nemard's happiness gives me happiness.
I am ready to move on.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev045101_MSG2001
rows.name:
Is it true Earth alien females wear special garments for
weddings?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev045101_MSG2002
rows.name:
I watched moving picture of "wedding dress."
I wanted to learn about making Earth-alien clothes.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev045101_MSG2003
rows.name: So lovely! I am in awe.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev045101_MSG2004
rows.name: I hope to have daughter one day.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev045101_MSG2005
rows.name:
When she takes mate, I will make fine white dress
for her. She will shine like sun![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev045101_MSG2010
rows.name: Other day, Nemard brought me lovely jewel as gift.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev045101_MSG2011
rows.name: I could not stop crying from joy.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev045101_MSG2012
rows.name:
If Nemard's next gift to me is child,
I might wash whole city away![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev045101_MSG2013
rows.name:
True happiness is force of nature.
Exciting, but also terrifying.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev045101_MSG3001
rows.name:
I went to your cathedral earlier.
Saw mysterious ritual for BLADE who died.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev045101_MSG3002
rows.name: Everyone wore thin black clothes. It was strange.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev045101_MSG3003
rows.name:
When Prone bury dead, we wear proper protection in
case of beast or Cavern Clan attack.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev045101_MSG3004
rows.name:
Otherwise, funeral can end with more funerals.
We would never wear such flimsy rags.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev045101_MSG3009
rows.name:
I realized something when I saw Nemard grieve
Grandfather.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev045101_MSG3010
rows.name:
I cannot always weep and expect him to hold family
together.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev045101_MSG3011
rows.name: I must find strength as Prone female and mother.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev045101_MSG3012
rows.name:
I will become great pillar. Strong as oak.
Then we will build family to make Grandfather proud![ST:wait ]
